g/wiki/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%259C%2583&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpPYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=1fa66b96\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83</a>"},{"pid":"814280228de5d990c023be8576c319e030ef9905","tid":1747624,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T10:18:42.000Z","msg":"當大家仲好有原則咁話個game唔公平<br />\n有大bug<br />\n唔投依個唔投嗰個<br />\n<br />\n甚至投保皇<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相信保皇同中共已開定香檳<br />\n統一戰線大成功<br />\n<br />\n用反間計離間計<br />\n<br />\n不戰而勝<br />\n<br />\n全世界傳媒，議員開哂口話今次係變相公投<br />\n世界各國傳媒喺香港 議員嚟觀察<br />\n<br />\n但香港人畢竟多政治白痴<br />\n喺受薪三毛 分化撚橫行嘅鋪天蓋地宣傳下<br />\n唔團結 好有原則 好冇策略<br />\n對住個狡猾同最叻玩政治，最叻分化嘅政權 <br />\n條路自己揀<br />\n仆街唔好喊<br />\n<br />\n唉 我只係覺得好可惜<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">如果輸咗<br />\n萬劫不復<br />\n<br />\n大家聽日早啲去投票<br />\n全家總動員<br />\nCall齊親友</span>"},{"pid":"ebc8cb62b473205fc36c62f9a971b7d2929838aa","tid":1747624,"uid":221265,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fa36b475c1645c8929c6408d5a52b8613711be2b","tid":1747624,"uid":241151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T10:05:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HTkS9bd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHTkS9bd.jpg&h=e423dd4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原來泛民平日係議會經常都益建制派！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T10:18:56.000Z","msg":"此人仍知名三毛"},{"pid":"a65a9b61175ceb2f6916ae9362721a31311a6b86","tid":1747624,"uid":272805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T10:19:31.000Z