lockquote><br />\n<br />\n<code>#1 - 改口號啦！[香港人！送頭！]<pre><code data-type=\"\">5f0a4355b76461506040117</code></pre>#1 - 點呀？之前係咪話過要追究返邊d人，邊d網，邊d團體同傳媒吹市去送頭既？</code><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1691882/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1691882/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T2b0VZQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT2b0VZQ.jpg&h=2ac5df0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原來係連登x蘋果吹雞<br />\n難怪有哂地點時間表<br />\n鑊鑊都港島，鑊鑊都推人去死<br />\n流人哋嘅血成就自己得票當選！<br />\n泛民蘋果全部都要仆街冚家鏟！<br />\n<br />\n好彩我一早就同班泛民左膠割晒蓆姐，分化實在好！<img src=\"http://lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n快d回&quot;拉，不分化，不推文回覆啦&quot;<img src=\"http://lihkg.com/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<code>#1 - 香港既和理非從來唔保護勇武，甚至會阻止勇武制服勇武出賣勇武，所以和理非實則係港奸</code><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1661812/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1661812/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<blockquote>泛民港奸！<img src=\"http://lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" /></blockquote>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T10:29:51.000Z","msg":"推回我，拉正文"},{"pid":"9a6837aeafca017fd7d10b6cd538648fd39a9f00","tid":1747624,"uid":241151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"814280228de5d990c023be8576c319e030ef9905","tid":1747624,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T10:18:42.000Z","msg":"當大家仲好有原則咁話個game唔公平<br />\n有大bug<br />\n唔投依個唔投嗰個<br />\n<br />\n甚至投保皇<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相信保皇同中共已開定香檳<br />\n統一戰線大成功<br />\n<br />\n用反間計離間計<br />\n<br />\n不戰而勝<br />\n<br />\n全世界傳媒，議員開哂口話今次係變相公投<br />\n世界各國傳媒喺香港 議員嚟觀察<br />\n<br />\n但香港人畢竟多政治白痴<br />\n喺受薪三毛 分化撚橫行嘅鋪天蓋地宣傳下<br />\n唔團結 好有原則 好冇策略<br />\n對住個狡猾同最叻玩政治，最叻分化嘅政權 <br />\n條路自己揀<br />\n仆街唔好喊<br />\n<br />\n唉 我只係覺得好可惜<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">如果輸咗<